quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  12,1,"Alif. Lam. Ra'. These are the verses of a Book that clearly expounds the truth."
  12,2,"We have revealed it as a Recitation in Arabic that you may fully understand."{1}{2},footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2
  12,3,"(O Muhammad), by revealing the Qur'an to you We narrate to you in the best manner the stories of the past although before this narration you were utterly unaware of them."{1},footnotes:1:1
  12,4,"Call to mind when Joseph said to his father: "My father! I saw (in a dream) eleven stars and the sun and the moon: I saw them prostrating themselves before me.""